Creates an Okta User.

This resource allows you to create and configure an Okta User.

## Example Usage
{{% example %}}

```typescript

import * as okta from "@pulumi/okta";

    description: "My custom property name",
    index: "customPropertyName",
    master: "OKTA",
    scope: "SELF",
    title: "customPropertyName",
    type: "string",
});
```
